name: Millennium Falcon™
description: A legendary starship despite its humble origins and deceptively dilapidated exterior, the Millennium Falcon™ has factored into some of the Rebel Alliance™ greatest victories over the Empire™. Before Han Solo™ won it in a game of chance, it was owned by Lando Calrissian™. Solo™ and first mate Chewbacca™ flew the Millennium Falcon™ into cinematic history.
